# JVM crash dumps — left behind when a Gradle/Kotlin daemon is killed.
hs_err_pid*.log
replay_pid*.log
*.apk
*.aab
/app/build/

# Internal working docs — not part of the shipped source.
/spec.md
/PHASES.md
/tested.md
/tested2.md
/idea.txt
/image.png

# Release signing — never commit these.
# The keystore IS your app's identity on Play: leak it and someone else can ship
# a "PaperCut update"; lose it and you cannot update your own app (Play App
# Signing softens that, but only if you enrol). Back it up somewhere safe and
# offline.
/keystore.properties
*.jks
*.keystore
